16. Beguardos] See Ep. 843. 62011. Egmondanus, Beda, and the Paris Censurae seem to have taken pleasure in noting Erasmus' affinities with the Beghardian heresim, particularly in respect of the view that the spiritual man is not bound by forms or cere- monies.
